name: F**K! WHERE ARE MY KEYS?!?!
description:
This game was made for the  #ggjonline with the topic "Lost and Found" and is part of the #ggjsh.

F**K!

You lost your keys...
and you don't have any time left!
- Search everywhere
- Shake everything
- YOU DON'T HAVE TIME!

Use WASD to move and LMB to interact with objects.

Made by:

Christian -Samb- Wasser - Game Design, Programming

Alexander Sahling - 3D Art 

Melanie Sidthiphol - 3D Art 

Ben Zimmermann - 2D Art, Music, Sound
